snippet.title: Into Evil - Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1893440/INTO_EVIL/

Early access coming soon!

It's been 1 YEAR (and a few days, but who's counting) of development on INTO EVIL!

MUCH remains to do, but much has also been done! And to commemorate that, here is the FIRST TRAILER!

Many things await in 2023!



"Black Vortex" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
